Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken a real turn for the worse since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken him to a number of doctors,\Nbut the cause is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone from a caravan fleet\Nthat makes stops at countries around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking perhaps you'd know\Na good way to treat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may... I am just a pharmacist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's get him to the caravan's medical ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we need to get his fever down,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,or else his body will be permanently damaged\Neven if he does survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Kiyui doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to head to the caravan fleet for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of things here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyui...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so very much looking forward to\Nhis birthday celebration today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... He can't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Birthday-Death Disease"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, an awful lot of people have died\Non the same day of the year they were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a rumor going around\Nthat it's the work of some disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The deceased's ashes are returned to the Abyss\Ntogether with Eternal Fortune flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That funeral is for someone\Nwho passed away from this same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, before this child got sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,two others at the orphanage died\Ndue to some unknown medical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting suspicious deaths alone, the total is five now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were orphans\Nwhose birthdays were unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something as absurd as all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think it's just a stupid made-up story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you alright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What could this possibly mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy is so healthy\Nit's hard to believe he even had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, I suppose it is some kind of curse or spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, there's been something\Nlike it before - something completely absurd...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious "Great Pit of the Netherworld,"\Nwhich is itself referred to as a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Longing seizes people more powerfully than poison\Nand more deeply than illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it catches hold of you,\Nthere is absolutely no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quite a "curse," and yet the adventurers\Nall willingly devote themselves to its pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For them, a life without longing\Nis more terrifying than death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Daremo ga sakaraezu ni mogutteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono me o tomoshibi yori kagayakasete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezasu saki wa fukaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Massugu ni mayoikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiaketa naraku no wana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu no ato o oikakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kotae ga mitsukaru nara zenbu nakushitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono koe o hanasanai youni kodama ga mada hibiiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashinban wa zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami o sashita mama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeba no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore ga noroi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodou wa honmono
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nidoto akogare wa tomaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the scenery of somewhere similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that was one of my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,my own memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, the one\Nwho was mourning for Lyza was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I bury her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ozen said, "No one was buried there."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it all mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,S-stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop it! You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty won't attack humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally Mitty doesn't get emotionally attached\Nto visitors, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're close in age, so maybe Mitty\Ntook a liking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Before becoming like this,\NMitty was also a girl, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mitty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please don't eat the mushrooms, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not one to treat others so cruelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to Mitty, after all,\Nthat we got the poison out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That medicine was made by injecting Mitty\Nwith an orbed-piercer's poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty has the ability to neutralize poisons all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I then used her blood\Nto produce the medicine, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, who exactly were you two\Nbefore you became Hollows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You really wanna ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you're gonna end up wanting to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll try to help-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My special Netherworld Stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like sticky... mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This... was made with the ingredients I collected, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about, um, how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It has an oddly fishy scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck kinda smell is that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take some for you too, Mitty,\Nso you can munch on it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of discharge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this truly made using those ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You... think it's bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, you normally eat this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't look at me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Look, I've never even gotten to eat\Ntasty food before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Riko wakes up and eats this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this time she's really going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice! I have to cook myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... if you don't like it, don't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's looking for her mother who descended\Nto the bottom of the netherworld, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we're talking about a girl\Nwith an insatiable curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and a piece of junk who can't regain\Neven one of his important memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well just making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say, it was actually quite hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of a way to evade\Nthe Curse of the Abyss, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I was to explain it\Nto someone like you who can't "see" it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's also my personal secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! We need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's in my power, I'll do whatever you want in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make an exception\Nand let you experience it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you get under here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fog Weave," a grade-3 Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's basically a super thin piece of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like this, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The true nature of the Curse of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's floaty in the same kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With layer piled upon layer, it blankets us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you touch it, you won't feel it,\Nnor can you see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When we move, it moves along with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply breathing is enough to alter its flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so when you touch it,\Nthat's when you're hit by the Curse of the Abyss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you touch it, it simply warps...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So then what makes you get hit with the Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be... doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda like... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you break through,\Nthe symptoms hit you all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just something like your fingertips,\Nyou'll hardly be affected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to your head or chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If any part of you that's vital to life\Npasses through, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you've seen, something seriously\Nnot good will end up happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what happens when you descend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, passing on through from above is nice and smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a flow to it similar to "inverted thorns,"\Nmaking it so you can't get out once you've entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. It's something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a trap for catching prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That malice-filled floaty thing, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that carries light to the subterranean world\Nwhile at the same time obstructing observation of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that continues to stubbornly guard the\Nnetherworld's true nature and the order within it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mysterious force field I speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Filling every corner of this pit,\Nit's the very blood of the Abyss, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the true nature of the Curse of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to escape from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, Nanachi, didn't you say the Curse\Nwasn't present around your hideout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I took great pains to find this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The force field gets weaker the farther away\Nyou get from the vertical shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After descending this far,\Ndon't you have somewhat of a feel for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose there aren't many places\Nas stable as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That area around the Seeker Camp also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the force field is sensitive\Nto the movements of living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It even responds to their very consciousnesses\Nand alters its flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can read something's consciousness,\Nyou can anticipate its movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Orbed-piercers don't have great intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They can actually predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The deeper you go, the denser and stronger\Nthe force field becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So challenging the netherworld's bottom means\Ncontinuing on a path brimming with a deadly curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,while also going up against predators\Nthat can predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds positively delightful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how in the world do cave raiders\Nmanage to still press on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? They aren't even able to see it,\Nso I wonder myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there is one thing I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the way it is.\NThere's no way to stop their longing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know. Hand me your helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that I'd let you experience it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, you have to promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to do exactly as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kinda unsettling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, it feels like you're right next to my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?\NIt's just something I happened to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear your voice,\Nbut where exactly are you, Nanachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I can see you fine from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't needlessly rush in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-? A child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Black Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the stuff he was carrying, he was\Nheaded back on his own when he got ambushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try rescuing our new visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter happens, you do exactly as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you'll be able to dispose of Orby\Nand the man will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll show it to you now: the world as I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, to start, look up and completely commit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen, really commit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hurry and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, stop questioning me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My orders are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now jump to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Irredeemable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You grabbed onto it, I see. Absolutely do not let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing you've grabbed onto\Nis the organ it uses to sense the force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's its lifeline, and without uncoupling\Nyour actions from your conscious mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never be able to even touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's confused, it'll go for the kill\Nwithout any thought of looking graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Tie it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Its fate is sealed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shed its spines?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This steam is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-did it escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was forced to eject a full 80 percent of its spines.\NIt won't be able to hunt here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, hurry up and get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey! Don't get too close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Orby is gone, it's cave raiders\Nthat present the most danger to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you relay a message for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intended for a guy at\NBelchero Orphanage named Jiruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiruo... at Belchero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him that... "We are still continuing our adventure."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you didn't tell him about me,\Nso I don't really mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure it'll be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That, uh, guy at Belchero Orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If people find out he's connected to you somehow,\Nit could spell trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the most dependable guy I know, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, that was pretty amazing, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the opponent's own special ability against it\Nlike that was a brilliant strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd come with us\Nto the bottom of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask anything of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be, but it truly is a hard thing to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please kill Mitty for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, I'm sorry for running away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't just let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,keep doing as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll figure something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora ni ukanderu hikaru nami o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanete niji no hashi o kakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaui ashiba, suberu slope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai no michishirube
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hidarite, boku no migite o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunaide tsunagete hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako mo ima mo mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakara mayowazu ni aruiteikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:23:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Irotoridori no yume kasanete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashita wa doko ni mukau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi to issho ni iretara, sekai wa kagayakidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Saihate no chi ni saku hana o sagasou
